	<td bgcolor="#000000" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" > <b>How I'd fix warriors...</b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >Just some thoughts I was having today...What would it take to fix the class? Well...I decided this is how I'd do it:<br />
<br />
1. DoT taunt<br />
2. Innate 25% Shielding - starting with 5% at level 30, 10% at 40, 15% at 50, 20% at 60, 25% at 65.<br />
3. Remove the defensive discipline. Keep the evasive discipline as it is.<br />
4. Innate 20% bonus on hp and ac for items with SHD and PAL on them.<br />
5. Unlock offensive discipline timers and bring their timers down to a minimum of 10mins, maximum of 25.<br />
6. Reduce the ability for a mob to riposte a warriors mainhand weapon by 50%<br />
7. Tactical Mastery / Strikethrough should not only hit through a riposte, it should prevent the riposte from ever occuring.<br />
8. Sta over 255 should follow the trend pre-255 (warrior only)<br />
9. Instant cast, 3minute re-use hate skill...200hate@lvl30, 300@40, 400@50, 500@60, 600@65.<br />
<br />
And for the nerfs...<br />
1. Take away the ability to taunt with spells that don't effect their target (stun, snare).<br />
<br />
That's about it.</font></p>
	
	<p></p>
	<p><font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" ><i>Last edited by Raaj on 11-09-2003 at 11:58 PM</i></font></p>
