<br />
I think that Warriors would also have less problem with what you guys call "snap aggro," if there was a reasonable mana(or time on raids) penalty for using it.  Warriors wouldn't need quite so many drastic changes if snap aggro was something that they had to use sparingly.</font></p>
	
